			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Choose Dark Urge in CC. Start game. In Camp debug book, Queue Camp Night, keep scrolling until you get to NIGHT_DarkUrge_MurderOfAlfira. Click on it, close the menu and end the day. Speak to Alfira, and this is the follow up if she stays the night." />
